    "bio": "AI Enthusiast | Automation Creator | Lifelong Learner\nHey there! 👋 I'm Gaurav, a Generative AI Specialist with a passion for making complex technology simple and accessible. Originally from India, I spent two amazing years in Rome earning my Master's in Data Science, where I fell in love with the intersection of AI, automation, and creative problem-solving.",
